member.summary:
Represents the method by which the minutiae data was read,
encoded, and recorded.

The following codes has been used:

0 - if coding method was not specified;

1- if the data was automatically read, encoded, and recorded
without any possibility of human

editing;

2 - if human editing was possible but unneeded;

3 - if the data was automatically read but manually edited
before encoding and recording;

4 - if the data was manually read.
